Model 1

Description of the model


Model 1 fits the flux between a prey (i) and its predator (j) only based on mass-action (biomass of prey and abundance of predators). The scaling parameters \(\alpha\) is general to every predator. \[\begin{align} F_{ij}^{real} &= \alpha * B_i * \frac{B_j}{M_j} \end{align}\]
